\toc1 Taruku ta Rut 
\mt1 RUT 
\imt1 An'…Ē Rut …Ēy…Ēn…õ-…õ, k…Ē t'ake t…Ē p…ômar pakaraŇč…õn…õ buk bamb…õ-…õ? 
\ip Buk bamb…õ, teta taruku ta aran m…õr…ôŇč t…Ē boloku. W…ôran w…ôl…Ēma k…Ē wos Ňčanay…õf…õ Yisrayel nde aŇčkom Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčand…õ nde at…Ēf Ňča Mohab. K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ wos efi k…Ē awut …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč d…ôndo Ňčanand…õ m…Ē. W…ôran nw…õ wos efi m…Ē, k…Ē aran m…õr…ôŇč aka awut …Ēn aŇč…õ Ňčafi m…Ē, Ňčayi oŇč sona d…Ēt…Ēf k…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka disr…õ. K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ wos efi m…Ē, …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôlukus nde at…Ēf nŇč…õ …õnay…õf…õ m…Ē. W…ôran ka wan k…Ēn nw…õ ancwe Rut, nw…õ …õnab…Ēt…ôr k…Ē haŇč m…Ē, …õnc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč k…ôk…Ē. Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ p…ôw…õy-w…õy mp…õ peŇčment…ôr k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ēn at…Ēy…Ē daka m…Ē. K…Ē Kanu k…ômar aran akaŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē k…ôwur…õ Ňča k…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka disr…õ nk…õ Ňčanayi m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčayi s…Ē sona m…Ē. 
\ip Taruku tant…õ t…õntam k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ afum a m…Ēk…Ē alar…ôm k…ôb…ôkn…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ a Kanu k…ômp…ôl…ôrn…õ Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē afum Ňčawos…õ k…ôc…ôm…õ Kanu dar…ôŇč Ňčacy…Ē m…õfaŇč m…Ēn-…õ, Kanu k…ôf…Ēp…ôl…ôr Ňča few. P…ôcucan…õ p…Ēl…Ēma p…õntam k…ôder, mba Kanu k…ôntiŇčk…ôli pi p…ôt…Ēt. D…ôk…ôcop da taruku tant…õ dement…ôr n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr, mba d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da pi, an…ôŇčk f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa Kanu k…Ē k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ēn nk…õ k…ônt…Ēlip m…Ē. Kanu k…ômar su k…ôc…ôr…õ ka tant…õ k…ôyi kosu doru f…ôp. Amina! 
\mt1 Taruku ta Rut 
\c 1  
\s1 P…ôl…õc…ôr pa afum a Elim…õl…õk 
\p  
\v 1 T…õm nt…õ aboc kiti Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr d…õb…õ da Yisrayel m…Ē, k…Ē dor dende deyi d…Ēt…Ēf. K…Ē fum w…ôka dare da Bet L…õh…õm nde at…Ēf Ňča Yuda, ende p…ôk…Ē nk…Ēn k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun m…õr…ôŇč, k…ôk…Ēcep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm nde at…Ēf Ňča Mohab.  
\v 2 Tewe ta fum w…ôkak…Ē t…õnay…Ēn…õ Elim…õl…õk, pacwe w…ôran k…Ēn Noyemi, k…Ē mewe ma awut …Ēn arkun akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…õnay…Ēn…õ Mal…ĒŇč k…Ē Kily…ĒŇč. F…ôp faŇčan aka kor ka ∆źf…ôrat Ňč…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ, dare da Bet L…õh…õm nde at…Ēf Ňča Yuda. K…Ē Ňčander at…Ēf Ňča Mohab k…Ē Ňčand…õ di.  
\v 3 K…Ē Elim…õl…õk wos ka Noyemi ende p…ôfi d…ôndo, k…Ē Noyemi eyi di oŇč k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 4 K…Ē awut akak…Ē Ňčande Ňčan…õnc…õ aran aMohab. W…ôran w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ancwe ∆Ürpa, k…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč ancwe Rut. K…Ē Ňčayi di meren w…ôco.  
\v 5 Mal…ĒŇč k…Ē Kily…ĒŇč Ňčande Ňčafi, k…Ē Noyemi ende p…ôyi oŇč, …Ēy…Ēf…õ w…ôrkun, …Ēy…Ēf…õ s…Ē awut. 
\s1 Rut k…ôc…ômb…ôr k…Ēn Noyemi Bet L…õh…õm 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Noyemi …õy…õf…õ nk…Ēn k…Ē aran a awut …Ēn dal…õ da Mohab, bawo analoku k…Ē d…ôndo dal…õ da Mohab a MARIKI …õmar afum …Ēn aka at…Ēf Ňča Yuda, k'ompoc…õ Ňča yeri.  
\v 7 K…Ē Noyemi …õy…õf…õ dal…õ dad…Ēk…Ē …õnayi m…Ē, k…Ē aran a awut …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k…ôlukus ka nde at…Ēf Ňča Yuda. 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē Noyemi oloku aran a awut …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč: ¬ęAwa, n…ôlukus nw…õ o nw…õ nde k…ôl…Ē ka iya k…Ēn! MARIKI p…ôy…Ēn…õ nu n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ônay…Ēn…õ ak…Ē Ňčafi m…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr k…Ē ina m…Ē.  
\v 9 Intolan…õ nu: MARIKI p…ôpoc…õ nu nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôforu nda w…ôrkun!¬Ľ K'oncup Ňča, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôbok.  
\v 10 K…Ē aran a awut …Ēn Ňčambup…ôr…õ: ¬ęAla! S…ôn'endek…Ē k…Ē m…ôna nde afum am Ňčayi m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē Noyemi oloku: ¬ęN…ôlukus aran a awut em! T'ake t…Ē n…ôndec…õps…õn'em dar…ôŇč-…õ? If…Ēs…Ētam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē awut aŇč…õ Ňčandetam s…Ē k…ôn…õnc…õ nu m…Ē.  
\v 12 N…ôlukus nde ndoronu aran a awut em, n…ôk…Ē! Bawo imb…õk oŇč w…ôrkun k…ôdes…Ēn…õnc'em. Ali icloku is…Ēr…õgb…õk…ôr Kanu amera, ali pibi pamp…õ p…Ē s…ôyi k…ôfo kin k…Ē w…ôrkun t…Ēy…Ēn'em k…ôkom s…Ē awut arkun-…õ,  
\v 13 n…ôndetam k…ôkar Ňča Ňčab…õk, n…ôndefat…õn…õ ti oŇč a pan…õnc…õ nu ba? Ala, awut em aran! P…ôl…õc mp…õ p…Ēs…Ēt'em m…Ē, poncu p…õtas p…Ēk…Ē p…Ēs…Ēt…Ē nu m…Ē, k…ôca ka MARIKI k…ômb…ôp im.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē Ňčambok s…Ē. K…Ē ∆Ürpa nk…Ēn oncup k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn Noyemi, k'elemb…ôrn…õ k…Ē, k'osump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k'…ĒŇčk…Ē. Mba Rut nk…Ēn owos…õ f…õ k…ôsak k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn Noyemi p…ôk…Ē.  
\v 15 K…Ē Noyemi oloku Rut: ¬ęM…ôm…Ēm…ôn w…ôres …ôm, olukus ndena afum …Ēn k…Ē canu c…Ēn. M…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēy…Ē m…Ē, m…ôna s…Ē m…ôk…Ē nde ndaram!¬Ľ  
\v 16 Mba k…Ē Rut oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa m…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôsak …ôm, m…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôlukus …ôm dar…ôŇč! Nde m…ôŇčk…Ē m…Ē, dif…Ē ina s…Ē indek…Ē. Nde m…ôndeyi m…Ē, ina s…Ē dif…Ē indek…Ēyi. Afum am, afum em Ňč…Ē. Kanu kam, Kanu kem k…Ē.  
\v 17 Nde m…ôndek…Ēfi m…Ē, dif…Ē indek…Ēfi, pawup im di. MARIKI p…ôy…Ēn'em ti, p…ôn…Ēc…ôr…õn'em nt…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ defi gb…ôc…ôr…ôm dendes…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôgb…õy…õn…õ k…Ē m…ôna-…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 18 Nt…õ Noyemi …õn…ôŇčk Rut …õŇčgb…ôc k…ôk…Ē k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē, k'…õsak k…ôloku k…Ē s…Ē teta k…ôlukus.  
\v 19 K…Ē Ňčasol m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan k…ôk…Ē haŇč k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ dare da Bet L…õh…õm. 
\p Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ Bet L…õh…õm m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônciyan…õ afum f…ôp te taŇčan. K…Ē aran ŇčaŇčyift…õn…õ: ¬ęNoyemi …Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ ba?¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē Noyemi oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ôw'em s…Ē Noyemi ¬ęW…ôyi d…ôp…ôbotu¬Ľ, mba n…ôcw'em oŇč Mara, ¬ęW…ôyi d…ôp…ôcuy¬Ľ. Bawo Kanu nk…õ k…ôntam mes ma doru f…ôp m…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč im p…ôcuy.  
\v 21 Nt…õ incy…õf…õ d…õ k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, waca wem w…õnalar…õ k…Ē MARIKI olukus'em waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr. Awa! N…ôsak k…ôw'em Noyemi, bawo MARIKI nw…õ …õntam mes f…ôp m…Ē, …õŇčkaf…ôl…ôrn'em, k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč'im p…ôcuy.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 22 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Noyemi …õnay…õf…õ dal…õ da Mohab k…Ē Rut w…ôMohab, w…ôran ka wan k…Ēn. Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ Bet L…õh…õm m…Ē, pat…õp k…ôccop k…ôt…õl ka m…õŇčg…õn m…Ēl…Ēma mm…õ amb…Ēf nde at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel m…Ē. 
\c 2  
\s1 Rut …ĒŇčk…Ē d…ôk…ôgb…õt…ôs at…õl a B…Ēs tadar…ôŇč 
\p  
\v 1 Noyemi …õnay…Ē w…ôkom…õn…õ ka wos w…ôl…Ēma. Fum w…ôka f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr …õnayi, p…ôy…Ē s…Ē daka. B…Ēs b'ancwe k…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē Rut w…ôMohab oloku k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn Noyemi: ¬ęM…ôwos'em ik…Ē nde dal…õ ik…Ē icgb…õt…ôs w…ôt…õl nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēwos'em k…ôyi k…Ē dar…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Noyemi oloku Rut: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē, wan kem w…ôran.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 3 K…Ē Rut …ĒŇčk…Ē d…ôk…ôgb…õt…ôs nde dal…õ at…õl tadar…ôŇč. K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ dal…õ nd…õ …õncgb…õt…ôs m…Ē da B…Ēs d…Ē, B…Ēs nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôkom…õn…õ ka Elim…õl…õk m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 4 P…ôwon f…õ k…Ē B…Ēs …õmb…õr…õ k…ôy…õf…õ ka Bet L…õh…õm. K…Ē B…Ēs eyif at…õl …Ēn, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęMARIKI p…ôsol…õ nu!¬Ľ K'at…õl Ňčantolan…õ k…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęAwa! M…ôna s…Ē, MARIKI p…ôpoc'am p…ôt…Ēt!¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē B…Ēs eyif fum w…ôk…Ē …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka at…õl …Ēn m…Ē: ¬ęAn'…Ēy…Ē w…ôyec…ôra nw…õ-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē w…ôb…õ ka at…õl …Ēn oloku: ¬ęWan w…ôran w…ôMohab …Ēf…Ē, nw…õ Ňčander k…Ē Noyemi, k…ôy…õf…õ ka dal…õ da Mohab m…Ē.  
\v 7 Nt…õ oloku m…Ē: ‚ÄĻN…ôwos'em ic…ôm…õ at…õl dar…ôŇč icgb…õt…ôs, icw…õts…õn…õ s…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn min min m…Ēk…Ē m…õnt…õmp…õn…õ toka dac…Ē m…Ē.‚Äļ K…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ enderna nn…Ē b…ôtb…ôt a k'…õnc…ôm…õ m…Ē, haŇč nd…õk…ôl. P…ôpic p'eŇčes…ômna nde d…ôk…ôl…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē B…Ēs oloku Rut: ¬ęM…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im belbel wan kem: Ta m…ôk…Ē s…Ē d…ôk…ôgb…õt…ôs tofo tocuru. Ta m…ôb…Ēl…õ s…Ē nn…Ē dal…õ dem, ta n…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ s…Ē ab…ôc em.  
\v 9 M…ôgb…ôtn…õ belbel nde ab…ôc em Ňčant…õl m…Ē, m…ôc…ôm…õ aran ak…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…õt…ôs m…Ē dar…ôŇč. M…ôn…ôŇčk iloku ab…ôc em, ta ŇčagbuŇč…õn'am. K…Ē domun dendenabas …ôm-…õ, m…ôk…Ē nde d…ôt…Ēb…Ēl, m…ôk…õt domun nd…õ ab…ôc em ŇčaŇčk…õt m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē Rut ontontn…õn…õ B…Ēs haŇč k'…õf…ônt…ôr…õ d…ônt…Ēf. K'oloku B…Ēs: ¬ęC…ôke c'iy…Ē-…õ, nt…õ m…ôndey…Ēn'em mam…õ, ina nw…õ iy…Ēn…õ w…ôcik…ôra m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē B…Ēs oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAl…Ēm…ôr im mi tin tin tin mes mm…õ m…ôy…Ē k…Ēnc…ôra kam, k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ wos …ôm efi m…Ē, t…Ēk…Ē m…ôsak papa kam, iya kam, k'at…Ēf Ňčam nŇč…õ aŇčkom …ôm m…Ē, m…ôcder nn…Ē nda afum aŇč…õ m…ônat…Ēc…ôr…õ t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 12 MARIKI p…ôlukus'am t…Ēk…Ē m…ôy…Ē m…Ē! MARIKI p…ôs…ĒŇč'am ti k…ôway, nk…Ēn Kanu ka Yisrayel nk…õ m…ônder m…ônd…õ kat…ôk…ôp k…Ēn d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē Rut oloku: ¬ęM…ômbaŇč im belbel, m…ôna w…ôb…õ kem! Moloku mam m…Ēs…ĒŇč'em ab…ôk…ôc k…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ, k…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē m…ôm…Ēm…ôn ti-…õ, ali w…ôb…ôc kam w…ôkin s…ôf…Ēt…ôŇčn…õn…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 14 Nt…õ t…õm ta k…ôdi yeri tendeb…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē B…Ēs oloku Rut: ¬ęM…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ m…ôdi yeri nn…Ē s…ôyi m…Ē, m…ôbaŇč k…ôcom, m…ôct…õm ki nn…Ē d…ôm…õnc.¬Ľ K…Ē Rut …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ at…õl k…ôs…ôk. K…Ē B…Ēs …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôcom, k'…Ēs…Ēm ki, k'…õn…õmb…ôr…õ, k'…õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ k…ôlp…ôs.  
\v 15 K…Ē Rut …õy…õf…õ s…Ē k…ôgb…õt…ôs, k…Ē B…Ēs oloku ab…ôc …Ēn: ¬ęN…ôce k…Ē s…Ē p…ôgb…õt…ôs nde d…ôtoka, ta n…ôm…Ēm…ôn…õn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 16 N…ôcwak k…ôcsul-sulu s…ôbomp sa m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēl…Ēma yati n…ôcgbal…õ k…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôcw…õt…ôs si m…Ē, ta n…ôcm…Ēm…ôn…õn…õ k…Ē, ta n…ôloku k…Ē t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē Rut …õŇčgb…õt…ôs haŇč d…Ēf…Ēy, k'…õs…õp…ôr m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēk…Ē …õnagb…õt…ôs m…Ē, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn ma …Ērs ab…õk Ňčin. 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē Rut …õl…õk m…õŇčgb…õn mm…õ k'…õsar…õ, k'eŇčkek…ôr…õ mi, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôment…ôr k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn. K'owur…õ s…Ē yeri y…Ēn y…õlp…ôs, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē.  
\v 19 K…Ē k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn eyif k…Ē: ¬ęDeke m…ôŇčgb…õt…ôs m…õŇčgb…õn mm…õ f…ôp m…Ēk…Ē-…õ? Dal…õ d'ana d…Ē m…ômb…ôcna-…õ? Kanu k…ômar nw…õ …õŇčk…õk…ôs…ôn'am m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\p K…Ē Rut oloku k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn: ¬ęAb…Ēf Ňča w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma Ňč'imb…ôcna, pacwe k…Ē B…Ēs.¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē Noyemi oloku w…ôran ka wan k…Ēn: ¬ęIn…ôŇčk MARIKI nw…õ …Ēs…Ēr…Ēlas…õ s…ôna ayi doru n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr, p…ôm…Ē ak…Ē Ňčafi m…Ē. Kanu k…ôpoc…õ w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ p…ôt…Ēt.¬Ľ K…Ē Noyemi oloku k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęW…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē, w…ôkom…õn…õ kosu …Ēf…Ē! Ňäa Ňč…Ē p…ômar Ňčac…ôm…õ su d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ  
\v 21 K…Ē Rut w…ôMohab oloku s…Ē: ¬ęOlok'im s…Ē, m…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ ab…ôc em haŇč Ňčalip k…ôt…õl'em f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Noyemi oloku Rut w…ôran ka wan k…Ēn: ¬ęWan kem p…ôntes…õ ti tat…Ēk…Ē, n…ôsump…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē ab…ôc …Ēn, ta m…ôtor dal…õ da nw…õ o nw…õ nde aŇčk…Ēt…Ērs'…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 23 K…Ē Rut Ňčasump…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē ab…ôc a B…Ēs k…ôgb…õt…ôs haŇč k…Ē k…ôt…õl ka m…õŇčgb…õn ma …Ērs k…Ē c…ôgbay k…ôlip\f + \fr 2:23 \ft  M…õŇčgb…õn mowur…õn…õ mal…Ē, mm…õ aŇčwe databo ¬ęorge¬Ľ m…Ē.\f* k…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn ma d…ôm…Ēr…Ē.\f + \fr 2:23 \ft  Mal…Ē mm…õ aŇčwe c…ôtabo ¬ębleŐĀ¬Ľ m…Ē, mi m…Ē aŇčlomps…õ ¬ęfarine¬Ľ.\f* Ňäas…Ēr…Ēyi k…ôfo kin k…Ē k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn. 
\c 3  
\s1 Rut k…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ pibi nde w…õc…ôk wa B…Ēs tant…Ēf 
\p  
\v 1 Noyemi k…Ēnc…ôra ka Rut, oloku k…Ē: ¬ęWan kem, ifaŇč k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm w…ôrkun p…ôn…õnc'am, m…ôna s…Ē m…ôŇčes…ôm, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôb…Ēt s…Ē m…ôna m…Ē.  
\v 2 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, B…Ēs nw…õ …õsak …ôm m…ôcb…ôc k…Ē ab…ôc …Ēn m…Ē, m…ôlaŇč ti oŇč a fum kosu …Ēf…Ē? M…ônc…ôr…õ s…Ē a pibi pa m…Ēk…Ē p'aŇčk…Ēfoy nde kur k…Ēn m…õgb…õn ma …Ērs mam…Ēk…Ē anat…õl…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 3 M…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôsop…õ moro, m…ôb…õrn…õ duma m…ôk…Ē d…ôndo aŇčk…Ēs…õp…ôr…õ k…Ē m…Ē! Ta m…ôwur…ôr k…Ē ta …õntalip k…ôdi yeri k…Ē k…ômun de!  
\v 4 K'endena p…ôck…Ē d…ôk…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ-…õ, m…ôgb…õk…ôr…õ da …õŇčf…ônt…ôr…õ m…Ē. K…Ē m…ôy…õf…õ-…õ, m…ôk…Ē m…ôfeni k…Ē k…ôloto nde d…ôw…õc…ôk, m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ. Nk…Ēn B…Ēs yati …ĒŇčk…Ēlok'…ôm t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar a m…ôy…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Rut oloku k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn: ¬ęIŇčk…Ēy…Ē tant…õ m…ôlok'im m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Rut …ĒŇčk…Ē nde d…ôkur, k'…Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 7 K…Ē B…Ēs endi yeri, k'omun, k…Ē p…ômb…Ēt k…Ē d…ôris. K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ nde kur k…ôl…ôps…ôr m…Ē. K…Ē Rut …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôfeni k…Ē k…ôloto d…ôw…õc…ôk, k'…õmb…õr…õ, k'…õf…ônt…ôr…õ. 
\p  
\v 8 P…ôndeyi c…õk-c…õk, k…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ oyok…ôrn…õ, endekaf…ôl…õ: K'…õmb…ôp w…ôran p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…õc…ôk tant…Ēf!  
\v 9 K'eyif: ¬ęAn'…Ēf…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Rut oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēf…Ē, ina Rut, w…ôcar kam. M…ôkump w…ôcar kam dobol da duma dam, bawo w…ôc…ôm…õ kem d…ônt…Ēf m…ôy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē B…Ēs oloku: ¬ęMARIKI p…ôpoc'am p…ôt…Ēt wan kem w…ôran! M…ôment…ôr s…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr nn…Ē akom…õn…õ a k…Ēnc…ôra kam Ňčayi m…Ē p…ôtas d…Ēk…Ē m…ônament…ôr t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. Bawo m…ônc…ôm…õ f…õ at…õmp dar…ôŇč Ňčay…Ē daka, Ňčay…Ē f…õ daka.  
\v 11 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč wan kem w…ôran ta m…ônes…õ, nt…õ o nt…õ t…Ē m…ôloku, iŇčy…Ēn'am ti, bawo dare f…ôp d…õnc…ôr…õ a w…ôran w…ôka d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…ĒŇč m…ôy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 12 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, kance k…Ē p…ômar a ic…ôm'am d…ônt…Ēf, mba w…ôl…Ēma eyi nw…õ …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ dokom k…Ē wos …ôm p…ôtas ina m…Ē.  
\v 13 M…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ nn…Ē pibi. B…ôtb…ôtana, k'…õfaŇč k…ôl…õk k…ôc…ôm'am d…ônt…Ēf-…õ, tentes…õ, p…ôc…ôm'am d…ônt…Ēf. Mba k'…Ēnt…ĒfaŇč k…ôc…ôm'am d…ônt…Ēf-…õ, ina inc…ôm'am d…ônt…Ēf, k…Ē MARIKI owos…õ-…õ! M…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ haŇč dec d…Ēcs…Ēk.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē Rut …õf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…õc…ôk tant…Ēf haŇč k…Ē dec d…Ēs…Ēk, k'…õy…õf…õ p…ôpan-pan, t…õm nt…õ ant…Ētam k…ôcn…õp…ôl…õn…õ m…Ē. K…Ē B…Ēs oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa pac…ôr…õ a m…ôndersa nn…Ē d…ôkur de!¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē B…Ēs oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôcipi k…ôfak…ôl nk…õ m…ônc…ôpn…õ m…Ē, m…ôsump…ôr ki belbel.¬Ľ K…Ē Rut osump…ôr k…ôfak…ôl, k…Ē B…Ēs …õmb…õr…õ k…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn ma …Ērs tafala cam…ôt-tin, k'onuŇčk…ôr k…Ē, k…Ē B…Ēs …ĒŇčk…Ē dare. 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē Rut …ĒŇčk…Ē ndena k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn Noyemi. K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē tencep…ôrna-…õ, wan kem w…ôran?¬Ľ 
\p K…Ē Rut …Ēl…Ēm…ôr k…Ēnc…ôra k…Ēn mes m…Ēk…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 17 K…Ē Rut oloku: ¬ę∆Üs…ĒŇč im …Ērs k…ôfala cam…ôt-tin, p…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻTa m…ôlukus waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr ndena k…Ēnc…ôra kam!‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Noyemi oloku Rut: ¬ęM…ôyi nn…Ē, wan kem w…ôran, haŇč m…ôcc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē mes mam…õ mendel…ôps…ôr m…Ē, bawo w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ, …Ēf…Ēs…Ētam k…ônd…õ k'…Ēnt…Ēlip mes mam…õ m…Ēk…Ē-…õ!¬Ľ 
\c 4  
\s1 B…Ēs …õl…õk k…õ ka Elim…õl…õk 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē B…Ēs …ĒŇčk…Ē d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da dare daŇčan k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ. P…ôwon f…õ, Elim…õl…õk w…ôkom…õn…õ w…ôk…Ē B…Ēs …õnaloku a w…ôkak…Ē …õnaŇčkan…õ k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôc…ôm…õ ka Rut d…ônt…Ēf p…ôtas k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ encep…ôr, k…Ē B…Ēs ewe k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ m…ôde m…ônd…õ nn…Ē!¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …Ēnc…ĒŇčn…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ.  
\v 2 K…Ē B…Ēs …õl…õk afum abeki w…ôco dare disr…õ, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ônd…õ nn…Ē!¬Ľ K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčand…õ.  
\v 3 K…Ē B…Ēs oloku w…ôk…Ē p…ônamar a p…ôc…ôm…õ Rut d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ Noyemi …õy…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňča Mohab, k'…õfaŇč k…ôcam…ôs tofok…ôl ta ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…õnc kosu Elim…õl…õk m…Ē.  
\v 4 K'inc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč'am ti k…ôc…ôr…õ, ilok'…ôm ti: M…ôs…õp m…ôway di f…Ēr ya abeki a afum asu kiriŇč k…Ē afum acuru ak…Ē Ňčandet…ôŇčn…õ ti m…Ē! K…Ē m…ôfaŇč k…ôway di-…õ, m…ôway! K…Ē m…ônt…Ēs…ĒfaŇč di-…õ, m…ôs…ĒŇč'em ti k…ôc…ôr…õ, bawo sariy…õ sa k…õ kaŇčk…õ, k…Ē m…ôna m…ôy…õf…õ day-…õ, in'…Ē p…ômar ic…ôm…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ oloku B…Ēs: ¬ęIfaŇč k…ôway dal…õ dad…Ēk…Ē yati.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē B…Ēs endeŇč…ôr: ¬ęK…Ē m…ôway dal…õ Noyemi d…ôwaca-…õ, m…õn…õ m…ônas…ôr s…Ē Rut w…ôMohab, w…ôran ka w…ôfi. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta tewe ta w…ôfi t…Ēs…Ēl…õ k…õ kaŇčk…õ k…ôroŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ oloku: ¬ęK…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē-…õ, if…Ētam k…ôway k…õ nk…õ ta ideyam…ôs teta daka dem nd…õ iy…Ē m…Ē. M…ôl…õk sariy…õ sem sa k…ôwurus, bawo if…Ētam ina w…ôs…ôrka k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ ti.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 7 Awa, c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel, k…Ē afum ŇčandecaŇč…ôs k…ôway k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti Ňčas…ôkp…ôr…õn…õ daka d…Ēl…Ēma-…õ, w…ôkin oŇčwur…õ k…Ēfta k…Ēn p…ôs…ĒŇč ki w…ôk…Ē Ňčayi k…ôlomp…ôs mes m…Ē. T…Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē t…õnay…Ēn…õ t…õcaŇčs…õ moloku c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel. 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ p…ônamar k…ôway dal…õ nd…õ m…Ē, oloku B…Ēs: ¬ęB…Ēs, m…ôna m…ôway!¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ owur…õ k…Ēfta k…Ēn, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč ki B…Ēs.  
\v 9 Awa, k…Ē B…Ēs oloku abeki k…Ē afum f…ôp: ¬ęTeyi m…Ēk…Ē f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč, a iway Noyemi d…ôwaca daka nd…õ d…õnay…Ēn…õ da Elim…õl…õk, da Kily…ĒŇč haŇč k…ôb…ôp ka Mal…ĒŇč m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 10 Iwos…õ s…Ē k…ônas…ôr Rut w…ôMohab, w…ôran ka Mal…ĒŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pade pacwen…õ k…õ kaŇčk…õ w…ôfi m…Ē, ta pade p…ôl…ôrn…õ tewe ta w…ôfi aw…õnc aŇča dac…Ē dare dand…õ. N…ôy…Ēn…õ m…Ēk…Ē at…ôŇčn…õ a ti.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da dare k…Ē abeki Ňčaluks…õ: ¬ę∆źy, teyi m…Ēk…Ē f…Ēr yosu kiriŇč! MARIKI p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ m…ôyi k…ônas…ôr m…Ē p…ôyi p…ôm…Ē Leya k…Ē Ras…õl, aran aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčkom afum aka at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel m…Ē! Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm s…Ēk…ôt aka kusuŇčka ka ∆źf…ôrat dac…Ē, m…ôs…Ēt…Ē tewe nde Bet L…õh…õm!  
\v 12 MARIKI p…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm k…Ē w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ awut alar…ôm, MARIKI p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ afum aka k…ôl…Ē kam Ňčade Ňčayi p…ôm…Ē awut aka k…ôl…Ē ka Per…õs, aŇč…õ Tamar …õnakom…õ Yuda m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē B…Ēs …õn…õnc…õ Rut, k'omboc…ôrn…õ k…Ē. K…Ē MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Rut k…ôb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun.  
\v 14 K…Ē aran Ňčaloku Noyemi: ¬ęS…ôŇčkor-koru MARIKI! ∆Üs…ĒŇč…õ m…Ēk…Ē k'aŇčkom fum nw…õ endek…õk…ôs …ôm m…Ē. Kanu k…ôde k…ôpoc…õ wans…Ē kam p…ôdeb…õk tewe Yisrayel.  
\v 15 Endekaf…ôl'…ôm teyi, p…ôk…õk…ôs …ôm detemb…ôra dam disr…õ. Bawo w…ôran ka wan kam nw…õ …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr …ôm m…Ē, okom k…Ē. W…ôran ka wan kam nw…õ encep…ôr …ôm awut arkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Noyemi …õl…õk wan k'…õn…õkn…õ, nk…Ēn Noyemi …õnadusum wan w…ôkak…Ē.  
\v 17 K'and…õ a Noyemi Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē tewe, Ňčacloku: ¬ęNoyemi oŇčkom wan!¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčawe k…Ē Ob…õd. Nk…Ēn …õnay…Ēn…õ papa w…ôka Yese, Yese …õnay…Ēn…õ papa w…ôka Dawuda. 
\s1 Mewe ma atem a Dawuda 
\p  
\v 18 Mewe ma awut a Per…õs m…õm…õ: Per…õs okom H…õc…ôron,  
\v 19 H…õc…ôron okom Ram, Ram okom Aminadab,  
\v 20 Aminadab okom Nas…ĒŇč, Nas…ĒŇč okom Salm…ĒŇč.  
\v 21 Salm…ĒŇč okom B…Ēs, B…Ēs okom Ob…õd,  
\v 22 Ob…õd okom Yese, Yese okom Dawuda.